query:
SELECT s.id, s.name, s.code, s.userId, u.email 
FROM subjects s 
LEFT JOIN users u ON s.userId = u.id 
WHERE s.code LIKE 'OSC%' OR s.code LIKE 'TEST%' 
ORDER BY s.id DESC;
